   "source": [
    "### 🔷 Background — Khapra Architecture\n",
    "\n",
    "We implement the exact architecture from **Prof. Mitesh Khapra's CS7015 Lecture 10**:\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "x_t (note index)\n",
    "    │\n",
    "    ▼\n",
    "┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n",
    "│  Embedding:  e_t = W_embed · x_t       │   e_t ∈ R^d\n",
    "└─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n",
    "    │\n",
    "    ▼\n",
    "┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n",
    "│  SimpleRNN:                             │\n",
    "│  s_t = tanh(W·e_t + U·s_{t-1} + b_s)  │   s_t ∈ R^H\n",
    "└─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n",
    "    │\n",
    "    ▼\n",
